    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Converse With a Small Person </strong>is a narrative experience that will take around 2 hours to complete. It mainly consists of a conversation between you and an old friend you never really knew. It's your choice to find meaning in it and if you do, it will adapt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/c620645674def5f5529fa13cd77d6eb7.poster.avif?t=1769724052\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/c620645674def5f5529fa13cd77d6eb7.webm?t=1769724052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/c620645674def5f5529fa13cd77d6eb7.mp4?t=1769724052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Story Shaped By Conversations</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every choice you make influences what will happen, think of it as talking to an old friend you haven't seen in a while. If he was flat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/c9346825702c09fb6888aa177c7d4768.avif?t=1769724052\" width=800 height=74 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dialogue, Dialogue, and more Dialogue</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game heavily relies on you, the player, paying attention to what the little guy says. You cannot skip the text, so pay attention!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/c04496b41560b1c5b7405d15c1c5c32f.poster.avif?t=1769724052\" width=800 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/c04496b41560b1c5b7405d15c1c5c32f.webm?t=1769724052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/c04496b41560b1c5b7405d15c1c5c32f.mp4?t=1769724052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Talk a little Deeper</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose choices that you wouldn't otherwise and see what the little guy says. You might be surprised how much it resonates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/e23f4a44f85100af255d8bf22f113a21.poster.avif?t=1769724052\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/e23f4a44f85100af255d8bf22f113a21.webm?t=1769724052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/e23f4a44f85100af255d8bf22f113a21.mp4?t=1769724052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Immersive Environments Shaped by Your Dialogue</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whatever you choose to talk about, the environment will change into that area. Look around these environments but make sure to focus on the little guy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/4f5e6da8a44a21b6dfe19c4ee1ece310.poster.avif?t=1769724052\" width=800 height=222 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/4f5e6da8a44a21b6dfe19c4ee1ece310.webm?t=1769724052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3053690/extras/4f5e6da8a44a21b6dfe19c4ee1ece310.mp4?t=1769724052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
